### Core

- Expo SDK 53, React 19, react-native 0.79.3
- TypeScript 5.8
- Use react-native-gesture-handler
- zustand for state management
- Tankstank query for ****asynchronous state management
- React Navigation
- Zod for schema validation.
- Jest, React Testing Library and Playwright for testing
- eslint and pretteir

### Navigation & layout

- react-navigation , react-native-gesture-handler, react-native-reanimated for smooth gestures & animations
- react-native-screens, react-native-safe-area-context

### Single purpose UI modules

- @discord/bottom-sheet (bottom-sheet component)
- react-native-progress (progress bars/circles)
- @mattermost/react-native-paste-input (rich paste handler)
- react-native-qrcode-styled (QR code renderer)
- react-native-safe-area-context, react-native-root-siblings (overlays, toasts, portals)

### Icons & Typography

- @expo/vector-icons + @fortawesome/react-native-fontawesome
- expo-font for custom font loading